name: Asus ZenBook 15
summary: Powerful and sleek laptop for professionals.
description: The Asus ZenBook 15 is designed for professionals who need power and portability. With its Intel Core i7 processor, NVIDIA GeForce GTX 1650 graphics card, and 16GB of RAM, it can handle demanding tasks with ease.

name: Dell XPS 13
description: The Dell XPS 13 is a compact ultrabook that packs a punch. Its Intel Core i5 processor, Intel UHD Graphics 620, and 8GB of RAM ensure smooth performance for everyday tasks. The 256GB SSD provides ample storage for your files.

name: HP Pavilion Gaming Desktop
summary: Affordable gaming desktop with powerful specs.
description: The HP Pavilion Gaming Desktop is perfect for gamers on a budget. With its AMD Ryzen 5 processor, NVIDIA GeForce GTX 1660 Ti graphics card, and 12GB of RAM, it delivers smooth gaming performance. The 512GB SSD provides fast storage for your games.

name: Alienware Aurora R11
description: The Alienware Aurora R11 is a beast of a gaming desktop. Equipped with an Intel Core i9 processor, NVIDIA GeForce RTX 3080 graphics card, and 32GB of RAM, it can handle the most demanding games with ease. The 1TB SSD provides plenty of storage for your game library.

name: MacBook Pro 16
description: The MacBook Pro 16 is the ultimate tool for creative professionals. With its powerful Intel Core i9 processor, AMD Radeon Pro 5600M graphics card, and 64GB of RAM, it can handle intensive tasks like video editing and 3D rendering with ease. The 2TB SSD provides ample storage for your projects.

name: Powerful Laptop
summary: A powerful laptop for all your computing needs.
description: This laptop is equipped with the latest technology and offers exceptional performance.

name: High-Performance Desktop
summary: A high-performance desktop for demanding tasks.
description: This desktop computer is built for speed and reliability, perfect for professionals and enthusiasts alike.

name: Portable Tablet
